{"tid":610921,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［老母式拍攝手法］豪洗窮遊上西藏","createTime":"2018-03-30T12:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T19:21:18.000Z","uid":67699,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"62ecb0c15123b719df58288f7b9324d23ff7a46b","tid":610921,"uid":67699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T12:08:49.000Z","msg":"聽日就出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n豪洗係因為今次選擇全程包車由成都一直玩上西藏拉薩。四條友，每人除返開其實都幾金。<br />\n<br />\n雖然西藏鐵路被喻為一生必搭一次嘅，好似唔坐過就無去過咁。不過，上次返大陸搭左次長途火車，試過十五個鐘軟卧，完全係車上無所事事等時間過，訓完又坐坐完又訓⋯⋯返黎仲要比唔個咩咬到成腳都係，都係不了。<br />\n<br />\n重點係由成都上拉薩，走川藏線，個條318公路都係被稱為「最美進藏線」。不過條線個靚景都就快無，所以要去就快啲去。因為好多路段都係修緊路、起緊隧道，我諗一年之後都會唔同晒。<br />\n<br />\n比大家睇下網上搵到既相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/200556_bd631ed18ffdf96074d27e9e79c71034.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F200556_bd631ed18ffdf96074d27e9e79c71034.png&h=397a177d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/200621_62a2d7e1b0f8410e01ba8a9b708120ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F200621_62a2d7e1b0f8410e01ba8a9b708120ba.png&h=1e8f0fb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n路上再匯報，睇下網上啲相有無誇大，西藏係咪堅係咁靚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0499bc2a5498bb2f7e878d5965fdacee5da22e25","tid":610921,"uid":67699,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:18:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/214032_fdcba2993ecce08ed40f4599f0160a48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F214032_fdcba2993ecce08ed40f4599f0160a48.png&h=14ebfefb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成都周街都賣兔頭、兔腿<br />\n先賣一個十蚊個兔頭、十蚊一隻腳<br />\n一隻兔仔既生命先值幾廿蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成都名物，兔仔，都係唔好搞我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/221703_4b7c19bf3a8623ca294dda4a56dbec9c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F221703_4b7c19bf3a8623ca294dda4a56dbec9c.png&h=54c77a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有豬鼻，咁樣比人插住個鼻"},{"pid":"0cd4934bb1e9266cb93c7d1cfec2fdf7afe5b76a","tid":610921,"uid":124471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:20:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9df5f31d84dbc76b88281db57f7282e1bc263616","tid":610921,"uid":30123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:22:02.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c394aca5d02101a0f4cae85cf07a5289f82700c8","tid":610921,"uid":63362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主會去幾耐？"},{"pid":"2e4f722426ec92503299d5527dfd77e6a0578f47","tid":610921,"uid":67699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c394aca5d02101a0f4cae85cf07a5289f82700c8","tid":610921,"uid":63362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主會去幾耐？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T15:35:12.000Z","msg":"去十六日吖"},{"pid":"9376fa990a450e5834352ca96de5be372315e504","tid":610921,"uid":169752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:01:29.000Z","msg":"十卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dacb30906cf3e3e3e4f26d272bcc84919ea6ff","tid":610921,"uid":42582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:04:47.000Z","msg":"個豬鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f44a39d60688c64f39992643619520171e3748","tid":610921,"uid":25389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"75fc52cd69918f1478f1466d820b9cdf4ff5aa3b","tid":610921,"uid":26159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"lm 7月去<br />\n條路線同你一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打你搵藏人司機定成都司機？"},{"pid":"95dc929dad79753d1761764f5a6a98a3ef54f962","tid":610921,"uid":67699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75fc52cd69918f1478f1466d820b9cdf4ff5aa3b","tid":610921,"uid":26159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"lm 7月去<br />\n條路線同你一模一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打你搵藏人司機定成都司機？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T16:27:47.000Z","msg":"司機係漢人吖，但住係西藏十幾年<br />\n亦都做左十幾年旅遊司機"},{"pid":"c4ad24bcd06d2bbd944c7e3f0049c06b3bedc1c2","tid":610921,"uid":88651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T19:01:08.000Z","msg":"堅係咁靚<br />\n但要有心理準備d路係九曲十三彎"},{"pid":"676ff68ac3ae296fc0786511e14b812aac49a854","tid":610921,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T19:08:11.000Z","msg":"個豬鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cff67231174070c86b2770c862512e11fc36a9","tid":610921,"uid":67699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T02:36:41.000Z","msg":"依條係318川藏線既海拔圖<br />\n雖然中間有高山，但其實都係路過<br />\n真正會有強烈高山反應<br />\n都係因為長時逗留係高海拔地方<br />\n所以夜晚最易有高山反應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/31/102458_a6519d2d49daf93e39424cd9c2ba4fef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F31%2F102458_a6519d2d49daf93e39424cd9c2ba4fef.png&h=6f4fe471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上我地都係沿住依條路入，景點都係依啲<br />\n係加插多一個稻城亞丁"},{"pid":"bdcea5d98ccbfbf7c24d143a88d853c3131051ad","tid":610921,"uid":40790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T04:06:17.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"12befd75f6f73f24042103b37d6099a8d5441ce6","tid":610921,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:03:47.000Z","msg":"死圖喎喂"},{"pid":"171467d08c0067b43ef0e138f4cefee293bfbbec","tid":610921,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12befd75f6f73f24042103b37d6099a8d5441ce6","tid":610921,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:03:47.000Z","msg":"死圖喎喂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"樓豬自己嗰啲睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c958c3900ee9b0eb62477ed36f4e6e914ef241","tid":610921,"uid":67699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T00:04:22.000Z","msg":"由成都出發，第一站到咗瀘定<br />\n我哋嘅第一個景點就係瀘定橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個人就無咩歷史知識，唔係好知個歷史源由。話係國家級4A景點，其實咁講姐係要收門票費，盛惠10蚊人仔過橋費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/075513_1da5a061f0c7739c0122bac907100be6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F075513_1da5a061f0c7739c0122bac907100be6.png&h=90af125a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似無咩野，但中間係有隙縫既，可以直接望到下面條河，一邊行一邊望其實都有小小淆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/080123_56f39788218931cd7e9a28629bd8ffa5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F080123_56f39788218931cd7e9a28629bd8ffa5.png&h=900937e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fffa86cb813057b8033e9d2d6b8a0e2537b0e709","tid":610921,"uid":67699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"171467d08c0067b43ef0e138f4cefee293bfbbec","tid":610921,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12befd75f6f73f24042103b37d6099a8d5441ce6","tid":610921,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:03:47.000Z","msg":"死圖喎喂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"樓豬自己嗰啲睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T00:05:56.000Z","msg":"我自己睇到啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全部都死晒？"},{"pid":"b44ac1f35ab8131623dde1a24d787e7c9c0ae286","tid":610921,"uid":99086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fffa86cb813057b8033e9d2d6b8a0e2537b0e709","tid":610921,"uid":67699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"171467d08c0067b43ef0e138f4cefee293bfbbec","tid":610921,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12befd75f6f73f24042103b37d6099a8d5441ce6","tid":610921,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:03:47.000Z","msg":"死圖喎喂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T05:04:20.000Z","msg":"樓豬自己嗰啲睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T00:05:56.000Z","msg":"我自己睇到啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n全部都死晒？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T02:25:33.000Z","msg":"睇到"},{"pid":"e07f74d90b58fdb8228d94c285b174f777ea44da","tid":610921,"