mal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe032022182811250afb045fccfaf343b27ac57","tid":610921,"uid":11677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:17:44.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ef6037ebd1ef671d598b6d7c93585fe7c0568fb7","tid":610921,"uid":67699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"跟住就上到今日最高既地方 - 多折山<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/131834_c09f6341b883baf0ca687529b94e4a23.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F131834_c09f6341b883baf0ca687529b94e4a23.png&h=9ad9bee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海拔4298<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/132033_edc6e998231933102b511935e026fae5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F132033_edc6e998231933102b511935e026fae5.png&h=bd99ba5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由成都幾百海拔，慢慢上到四千幾<br />\n自己真係無咩反應，照跑照跳<br />\n不過好大霧，又落下雨<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/01/132906_67c1c660524abf0975ac1565d5cf3d08.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F01%2F132906_67c1c660524abf0975ac1565d5cf3d08.png&h=59a7de03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲雪高到去欄干<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n溶左嘅雪變成冰，極度冼腳<br />\n而且一下子上到咁高，自己又著唔夠衫<br />\n所以無上到頂，有啲可惜，但都無計"},{"pid":"5b3b566f8306f8da97d3b4e5be94031e227547fe","tid":610921,"uid":67699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef6037ebd1ef671d598b6d7c93585fe7c0568fb7","tid":610921,"uid":67699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:33:54.000Z","msg":"跟住就上到今日最高既地方 - 多折山<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img